Package blackbox.simulations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstantTrafficBackgroundExpirationSim
    This simulation explores the latencies experienced when the pool is exposed to a predictable, constant throughput, with or without background expiration.
    Sim  
    TimeSpreadExpirationSim
    This simulation examines the difference that using TimeSpreadExpiration, instead of TimeExpiration, can have on latency.
    VariableTrafficSim
    A simulation that explores how the pool reacts to periods of low activity.
